{"tid":1383609,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益」和理非發夢打仗時點支援前線既手足","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T17:35:09.000Z","uid":293914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7290a865ae218cd1e8991f8acf4a6623e9df34fc","tid":1383609,"uid":293914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"見到好多人食唔飽都要去行街仲要比狗咬，我呢個cd-rom真係忍唔住第一次出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一齊發下夢<br />\n<br />\n以下係我暫時諗到既小小方法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1）流動即場補給</span></span></strong>：好似欖球棒球比賽時啲啤酒妹一樣整啲熟食/飲料補給，有需要既人唔使退好多離開戰場都有得醫肚<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2）發夢既夜晚每個地鐵站設偵察人員</span></span></strong>：差唔多發完夢時即時報告狗出沒情況，等任何人唔使心慌慌可以安心番屋企<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">3）流動Wi-Fi 蛋人</span></span></strong>：一個月內發咁多次夢，每次出成日街上網肯定用爆曬學生哥啲data，如果有人隨身攜帶Wi-Fi 蛋並免費share，肯定會幫到即時資訊既流通<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">4）Live Google地圖</span></span></strong>：係前線往往同時間內收到大量信息，有啲手足未必熟悉果區，連附近街道名都未記得清楚。有時電視台提到狗既動向，需要即時通知到前線既手足。以下係例子，大家都用同一個map，哨兵一有消息就更新地圖標記，手足只要reload就睇到最新既狗出沒地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/edit?mid=1N2QvBlpN06U6l1vuNhBMEiYDgBWa7c6c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fedit%3Fmid%3D1N2QvBlpN06U6l1vuNhBMEiYDgBWa7c6c&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJb%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=8ff0c3d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/edit?mid=1N2QvBlpN06U6l1vuNhBMEiYDgBWa7c6c</a><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999..但以上既崗位和理非既手足都做得到<br />\n同埋仲有好多討論空間！如果有人都想出一份力，希望可以有方法一齊討論下！<br />\n<br />\nPs: 有冇支援/後勤tg group 可加？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPs2: 無知一問，新開既ac有冇得pm？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86971c1c8b9d3a31618a26462912dd491c754e